      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Seems fine, but I wonder if Nightly is the right choice here. It seems we want \"Continuous\", because that will actually give the exact revision, instead of some obscure meaning of \"some time in the day\", which will break when the builds are done more often per day, of less than once per day.\r\n\r\nSee also https://my.cdash.org/index.php?project=bitcoin-core&date=2026-05-07 for reference of some continuous nighly builds with revision.",
